{"tid":1452213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將呢個仆街政府啲仆街野推到全世界都知","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:35:54.000Z","uid":289733,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7f8b704871c6fa5d9387f00476a3f46fc3123f","tid":1452213,"uid":289733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:26:01.000Z","msg":"攪多次<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">眾籌</span></strong></span>係全世界報紙登報，有冇得諗??<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將呢個仆街政府啲仆街野推到全世界都知，呼籲外國經濟制裁香港</span></span></strong>，<br />\n登報內容 : <br />\n1. 黑警如同恐怖份子，係室內地方發射過期催淚彈<br />\n2. 近距離向示威者射頭<br />\n3. 公安混入黑警當中<br />\n4. 法治精神蕩然無存<br />\n5. 香港融入大灣區<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制早已名存實亡</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地自己亦堅持 星期五六日 bye buy day <br />\n<br />\n呢個仆街政府同我地打經濟牌，我地就同佢打返經濟牌。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後，勇武派嘅手足，你地係時候停一停，諗一諗，我地真係唔想再有人送頭，因為我地再輸唔起，我地真係一個都不能少</span></strong>"},{"pid":"50067da5f904f81c1a516e2a2cd749ef5d7f4d9d","tid":1452213,"uid":289733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:26:54.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e57bde47d2443b37fd63a4ee1fcf7631b46752d7","tid":1452213,"uid":275282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPTyrqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPTyrqo.png&h=c5d2d7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WASvtDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWASvtDL.png&h=556225b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vi51AiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvi51AiN.png&h=6b29caf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmRL1YP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F